HEADWORD: Pronominalize
<hw>Pro*nom"i*nal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To give
the effect of a pronoun to; <as>as, to <ex>pronominalize</ex> the
substantives <ex>person</ex>, <ex>people</ex>, etc.</as></def>
